snippet.title: Don't Starve: Reign of Giants Expansion Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Get Don't Starve: Reign of Giants:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/282470

Now fully released and available on Steam and Standalone! PS4 version is on the way. Stay tuned for more details. 

Want to discuss the expansion? Head over to our community forum!
